SANTON looked at BUMP and then TUCSON before he returned his gaze back
to the CR chamber. "No." SANTON said carefully. "Discontinue the
transmetal transformation." He said carefully.

Walking up beside them LEGACY looked at the readout, "It would have
been better for one of you to alert us to her changed condition." He
said carefully to TUCSON. "This process removes most of the biological
processes and this transformation could have terminated her pregnancy
had the automatic scanners not discerned her status."

The CR chamber began to power down.

(TAG)

- Preston
